Dialogue: 3,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fad(250,0)\an7\fnESG3SP5C\1c&H19000C&\pos(64,46)}{\fs45}委托书\N{\fs35}你也想一个人借完?\N为了评选出王都最佳搭档组合\N将以地区对抗的形式举办第二\N届借物赛跑比赛\N{\fs30}上届大会好评如潮,旨在决出最强搭档\N组合的借物赛跑今年也将回归!!\N是时候从王都各区选出的强手中,决出\N真正的最佳搭档组合了.\N大会前,西区代表选拔赛……
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\fscx600\fscy400\p1\1c&HBAD5E0&\3c&H120001&\an5\bord3\alpha&H80&\pos(252,170)}m 10 10 l 100 10 100 100 10 100
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.02,0:00:05.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}命运   沉沦与未来
Dialogue: 3,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑暗吞噬光明
Dialogue: 3,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.20,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.33,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚开! 滚开! 快滚开! 快滚开!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.33,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.08,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.29,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚开! 滚开! 快滚开! 快滚开!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.63,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.63,0:00:25.76,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在锈蚀的阴暗牢笼中  匿去身形
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.76,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寻求归宿
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.59,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我将灵魂托付予你
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以砸烂锁链  冲破这监牢吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.39,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与这窒息的世界搏斗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.60,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}永不言弃  奋战到底
Dialogue: 3,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.93,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以撕碎枷锁  冲破这牢笼吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.31,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与这窒息的世界搏斗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.06,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别让它夺走你的光芒 站起来吧！
Dialogue: 3,0:00:40.85,0:00:45.44,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}徘徊于虚无之地  发出执着的呐喊
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.73,0:00:50.15,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挣脱脚镣展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.66,0:00:53.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于时间的夹缝中被征召的灵魂
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.16,0:00:56.83,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}纵使一切皆被焚烧殆尽
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.83,0:01:00.46,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若能吞下这份苦痛
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.67,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便能驾驭黑暗
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寄宿于心中的答案
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.88,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在黑暗中逆转  照亮前路
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道你不是吗？ 寻找明镜之人
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,OP - CN - BG,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为何不去探寻你自己的路
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.34,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要守护你
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.31,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为你的眼眸呼唤着我
Dialogue: 3,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.72,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暗中宣战  至死方休
Dialogue: 3,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.39,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我活着的证明
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.39,OP - CN - BG,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重拾信念  屹立不倒
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.48,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.65,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚开! 滚开! 快滚开! 快滚开!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.56,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.36,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.36,0:01:27.53,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚开! 滚开! 快滚开! 快滚开!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:27.53,0:01:29.19,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru guru guru 给我滚开！
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.02,0:00:05.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Fate doom and future
Dialogue: 3,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}dark over light
Dialogue: 3,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.20,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.08,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.29,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.63,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.63,0:00:25.76,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錆びついたShadow Prison  姿潜めて
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.76,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行き場を探しては
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.59,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}So break out so break out
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.39,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}To battle the tension
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.60,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Never give up that fight!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.93,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}So break out, so break out
Dialogue: 3,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.31,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}To battle the tension
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.06,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't let it claim your light rise!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:40.85,0:00:45.44,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.73,0:00:50.15,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}足枷を解いて羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.66,0:00:53.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.16,0:00:56.83,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとしても
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.83,0:01:00.46,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飲み込んでしまえば
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.67,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闇を振り翳して
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.88,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闇中反転照らして
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Aren't you？明鏡探すの
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,OP - JP - BG - 1,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Won't you make yours？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.34,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.31,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その瞳に呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 3,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.72,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暗中宣戦 全身全霊
Dialogue: 3,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.39,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.39,OP - JP - BG,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.48,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.65,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.56,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.36,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.36,0:01:27.53,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:27.53,0:01:29.19,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Guru-guru-guru... Get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.25,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Shine day
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.25,0:22:00.59,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那一天我寻见了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.59,0:22:08.89,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}足以改变这世界的瞬间
Dialogue: 3,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.81,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可我
Dialogue: 3,0:22:10.81,0:22:19.86,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我对迈出新的一步
Dialogue: 3,0:22:19.86,0:22:23.57,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是有些恐惧
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.99,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}紧攥小小的手
Dialogue: 3,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.04,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}垂头不语的你
Dialogue: 3,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.59,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧  仰起脸让我看见
Dialogue: 3,0:22:35.59,0:22:39.42,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那澄澈的眼眸
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.42,0:22:43.05,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I need  I need
Dialogue: 3,0:22:43.05,0:22:46.39,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}映照未来的美梦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:46.39,0:22:50.60,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至抵达梦之彼岸
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.69,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与我并肩同行吧
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.69,0:22:58.23,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I need  I need
Dialogue: 3,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.78,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要守护这份心愿
Dialogue: 3,0:23:01.78,0:23:05.78,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇气之门
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.78,0:23:13.75,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在  已悄然开启
Dialogue: 4,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.25,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Shine day
Dialogue: 4,0:21:55.25,0:22:00.59,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この世界が変わるような
Dialogue: 4,0:22:00.59,0:22:08.89,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな瞬間を見つけたあの日
Dialogue: 4,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.81,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}でも
Dialogue: 4,0:22:10.81,0:22:19.86,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}まだ新しい一歩を踏み出すことが
Dialogue: 4,0:22:19.86,0:22:23.57,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少し怖かった
Dialogue: 4,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.99,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小さな手をギュッとして
Dialogue: 4,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.04,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俯いてた君
Dialogue: 4,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.59,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}さあ　顔を上げて見せて
Dialogue: 4,0:22:35.59,0:22:39.42,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綺麗な瞳で
Dialogue: 4,0:22:39.42,0:22:43.05,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I need　I need
Dialogue: 4,0:22:43.05,0:22:46.39,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}映す未来の夢
Dialogue: 4,0:22:46.39,0:22:50.60,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辿り着くまで
Dialogue: 4,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.69,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一緒に歩いてく
Dialogue: 4,0:22:54.69,0:22:58.23,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I need　I need
Dialogue: 4,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.78,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守りたいと願う
Dialogue: 4,0:23:01.78,0:23:05.78,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇気の扉
Dialogue: 4,0:23:05.78,0:23:13.75,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今　そっと開けたよ
